Motau SC as an investigator to conduct a forensic investigation into the
affairs of VBS.Advocate T Motau SC has been tasked with the key point of the
investigation which will establish whether any of the business of VBS was
conducted with the intent to defraud depositors and creditors of the bank.Advocate T Motau SC will also investigate whether VBS’s business conduct
involved questionable or reckless business practices - which may include material
non-disclosure or without the intent to defraud depositors and otherThe initial findings of an assessment by SizweNtsalubaGobodo
showed that VBS was “severely mismanaged” and there was reason to believe there
has been fraudulent reporting and manipulation of financial information. The findings formed part of an affidavit filed by the
central bank on March 29.This was relating to a court application initially launched
by Vele Investments, the majority shareholder of VBS.